cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper addresses the problem of multi-person tracking in complex environments using computer vision techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques for learning deformable spatial relationships between detectors, which suggests the possibility of it belonging to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of detectors and tracking algorithms also suggests the possibility of it belonging to cs.RO (Robotics). Finally, the paper involves the use of RGBD data, which suggests the possibility of it belonging to cs.MM (Multimedia).
